title: Episode 179: Dominic Monaghan
itunes:subtitle: Actor Dominic Monaghan (Lord of the Rings, Lost, Wild Things) joins Brendan and Bryan to talk about his new show 'Wild Things' on The Travel Channel, his life changing role in The Lord of the Rings and much more.
